  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: So Lichenia sent you. That means you are not here for books.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: The blue atlas is not a map of places. It is a ledger of promises.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Tell me what it has to do with the barista.
